  "title": "Pillowy Russian Haricot Beans Papillote",
  "description": "A weeknight Russian dish featuring haricot beans in a pillowy papillote, pungent and flavorful without being too difficult to make. Serve with rye bread and a dollop of sour cream for a hearty meal.",
